2019-12-16 02:18:40	energizer	that doesnt change anything
2019-12-16 02:18:49	OneSploit	but it won't hold more than 20 rows at once in memory I think
2019-12-16 02:19:16	energizer	you can do read_row_group, but if i were doing this i would consider just getting a really big node
