2019-12-16 08:36:02	Yhg1s	Mrbuck: list.pop is not O(1) unless you're strictly popping from the end.
2019-12-16 08:36:23	Yhg1s	Mrbuck: your list comprehension has one loop it in, and it visits all the items in the list, so it's O(n).
2019-12-16 08:36:24	Mrbuck	Yhg1s: yes thast why I am making sure to pop from the end
2019-12-16 08:36:36	Mrbuck	but above its taking time
