2019-12-17 12:21:17	Widdershins	there are fairly few languages that even claim to show graphemes except in dedicated third party libraries, because it's largely indeterminate until the client library wants to render it, at which point it's up to them
2019-12-17 12:21:43	dunpeal	thevishy: what's unclear?  as a Python programmer, you just care about the Python interface of objects
